\pard\ql\b Reports\b0\par
\pard\ql The repository does not define a formal report engine (PDF/CSV analytics reports). User-visible statuses are presented as UI feedback (upload progress, activity states, message updates).\par
\page
\pard\qc\b 6. TESTING\b0\par
\pard\ql\b Introduction (Brief write-up about Software Testing)\b0\par
\pard\ql Software testing in ChatBhar focuses on validating key journeys: app shell rendering, chat stability, message sending fallback, and post viewer interactions.\par
\pard\ql\b Test Reports\b0\par
\pard\ql Existing verification scripts indicate end-to-end browser checks using Playwright (JavaScript and Python variants).\par
\pard\ql\b a) Unit Testing\b0\par
\pard\ql Dedicated unit test suites are limited; project verification is primarily behavior-driven UI testing.\par
\pard\ql\b b) Integration Testing\b0\par
\pard\ql Integration-style tests validate interactions between localStorage data, API fallback logic, and UI rendering.\par
\pard\ql\b c) System Testing\b0\par
\pard\ql End-to-end scripts cover full user flows such as opening chat, sending message, and interacting with feed/post viewer components.\par
\page
\pard\qc\b 7. CONCLUSION\b0\par
\pard\ql ChatBhar is a capable prototype unifying social publishing and messaging. Its dual-mode execution (backend + local fallback) makes it suitable for demonstration, experimentation, and staged product hardening.\par
\page
\pard\qc\b 8. LIMITATIONS\b0\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Local mode storage limitations for large media\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Cloud features depend on valid Firebase configuration\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Security, rate limiting, and production observability are not fully hardened\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Formal analytics/report export modules are minimal\par
\page
\pard\qc\b 9. SCOPE OF ENHANCEMENT (FUTURE SCOPE)\b0\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Production-grade backend/database with scalable media pipeline\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Role-based access and advanced moderation\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Notification services and mobile push integration\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Advanced analytics dashboards and exportable reports\par
\pard\ql\pntext\f0 -\tab{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf0\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}Native mobile clients using shared APIs\par
\page
